>What is it about the mechanicals (not the obvious aerodynamic issue) that
>causes a bus to be tossed about in wind

The bus is tall AND narrow. Add a rear sway bar and you'll reduce the buffeting some but not all.

The sidewall of your tires is also a factor. 

